Miami boarding at gate 33.

58
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,111
He thinks we'll let him
get away with that?

59
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,833
Depose Henry.

60
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,633
Sure.

61
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,433
I'll see you.

62
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:25,950
Sergeant...

63
