85
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:43,430
National Safety Board officials
were en route to the site...

86
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,391
--over Chesapeake Bay,
20 miles south...

87
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:05,314
